BREAKING: Florida continues its trend of surging daily COVID numbers with 2,016 new cases— our 2nd highest daily total on record. Highest total was reported yesterday 6/13. Meanwhile, @OrangeCoFL, Osceola, & Seminole each had their worst day on record. 😷
https://t.co/NLWCNvyi4j
